    <abstract id="aspace_487f96550665393dfd4173a725fe35b9" label="Abstract">The Larry Silver Photograph Collection consists of 58 gelatin silver prints of New York City, mainly Manhattan and the Bronx, taken between 1949 and 1989. The majority of the photographs are from the early 1950s.</abstract>
